{"tid":1604884,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［重post］所有人跟我方法做 我要聽日所有被捕者一定有律師支援","createTime":"2019-09-30T06:03:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T12:57:27.000Z","uid":147636,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8150625cc72506a3e408bacace086806d582c9b6","tid":1604884,"uid":147636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:03:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">［TG功能］就算你真的被捕了 手足都一定知你身份嘅方法！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1603475\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1603475</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n琴日上唔到熱門！！<br />\n幫我推俾所有手足！！<br />\n不論和理非定前線都要知道！！</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">TG 有個功能叫 <strong>Schedule Message</strong>!!<br />\n係一個可以排程發放Msg嘅功能！！</span><br />\n<br />\n聽日所有發夢家注意！！<br />\n請你出門前排程一個個人資料嘅Msg俾手足<br />\n可以係公海 你嘅特別小組 星火admin<br />\n設於聽日晚上發放</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><ins>萬一你已被捕<br />\n當晚你的個人資料會自動發放俾手足<br />\n<em>（關閉手機不影響此功能）</em><br />\n然後手足會自動波幫你搵律師同你嘅緊急連絡人<br />\n<br />\n如果沒有被捕 你當晚已安全回家<br />\n可以刪除已排程的個人資料<br />\n以確保身份保密</ins></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例子：<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"color: orange;\">［Scheduled Msg］<br />\n我可能已被捕！！<br />\n全名：陳大文 CHAN Tai Man<br />\nHKID： A123456(7)<br />\n個人手機：12345678<br />\n緊急人聯絡電話：87654321 (親大佬）<br />\n備註：請找星火/612基金！！</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n設立Schedule Msg教程：<br />\n（一）出門前 於某些tg gp的訊息欄輸入個人資料 然後<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">長按發送鍵</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yLeXMUa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyLeXMUa.jpg&h=0bfcdff8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（二）按Schedule Message<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3w1LbkW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3w1LbkW.jpg&h=42976fc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（三）<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">設定當晚發放時間</span></strong> 例如10月1 號的凌晨<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nRzg2sH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnRzg2sH.jpg&h=93ec7228&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（四）已排程的訊息會自動存儲於 Scheduled Messages Box<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WRaPC07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWRaPC07.jpg&h=61538ce9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LA1y4Ge.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLA1y4Ge.jpg&h=17ea6e64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（五）<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">如你已安全回家，你可以按一下訊息<br />\n然後立即刪除已排程訊息</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fVFzO72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfVFzO72.jpg&h=a91425ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再講<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">謹慎發夢 ！！！<br />\n設立Schedule Message！！！<br />\n唔好偷懶！！！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我要聽日所有被捕者都有律師支援！！！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>祝各手兄武運亨昌 平安歸來</strong></div>"},{"pid":"0a4ff4e68d4a03c1ba8ea6a7fbecdbd9b4fdaffb","tid":1604884,"uid":147636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:04:07.000Z","msg":"10.1 街上見"},{"pid":"6403eec03c8a399476caccb9e90443f08ffba742","tid":1604884,"uid":147636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:05:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f6ffb16ea54aea083c45e240e80fc44fa39d76c7","tid":1604884,"uid":147636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:05:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"56aee3b4c58db3b0f8758f3866039e6072f20f3e","tid":1604884,"uid":147636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:06:23.000Z","msg"